1- Flutter web can't load network image from another domain:
    flutter run -d chrome --web-renderer html // to run the app
    or:
    flutter build web --web-renderer html --release // to generate a production build
    read more: https://stackoverflow.com/questions/65653801/flutter-web-cant-load-network-image-from-another-domain?newreg=4fac51bbad2f43fa8877314c9055dd90
    or:
    beside the run button in Android Studio, click the configuration button (click on main.dart)
    edit configurations
    add this to the additional run args: --web-renderer html
    then run normally by clicking on the run button
